org.apache.flex.swc.io

Class SWCReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swc.io.SWCReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISWCReader

    public class SWCReader
extends Object
implements ISWCReader
    Read a SWC file using Java ZIP utilities. The SWCReader owns the result ISWC object.

      • getReportingPath

        public static String getReportingPath(String swcPath,
                      String libraryPath)
        Create a single path that is a combined path of the SWC and the library inside. This path should only be used for error reporting. It should not be used to open the file.
        Parameters:
        swcPath - the path of the SWC.
        libraryPath - the path of the library withing the SWC.
        Returns:
        combined path for SWC and library file.
